width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\"><img alt=\"Maru Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/23/Maru_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\">Maru</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\"><img alt=\"Pam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Pam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\"><img alt=\"Pierre Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/cf/Pierre_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\">Pierre</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\"><img alt=\"Robin Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d1/Robin_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ancient_Seed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ancient Seed is not used in any <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">bundles</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipes\">Recipes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ancient_Seed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Recipes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Ingredients\n</th>\n<th>Recipe From\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Ancient_Seeds.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Ancient Seeds.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/ec/Ancient_Seeds.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Ancient_Seeds\" title=\"Ancient Seeds\">Ancient Seeds</a>\n</td>\n<td>Could these still grow?\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Ancient Seed.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/af/Ancient_Seed.png/24px-Ancient_Seed.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/af/Ancient_Seed.png/36px-Ancient_Seed.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/af/Ancient_Seed.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ancient Seed</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</td>\n<td>Donating <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ancient Seed</a> to the <a href=\"/Museum\" title=\"Museum\">Museum</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ancient_Seed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ancient Seed is used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <a href=\"/File:Shirt237.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt237.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/9f/Shirt237.png/24px-Shirt237.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/9/9f/Shirt237.png 1.5x\" /></a> <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Brown Suit</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ancient_Seed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ancient Seed is not used in any <a href=\"/Quests\" title=\"Quests\">quests</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ancient_Seed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-cosmeticplant_performtoolaction-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-cosmeticplant_performtoolaction_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>StardewValley.TerrainFeatures.CosmeticPlant::performtoolaction</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Ancient_Seed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Updated sprite, added <a href=\"/Artifact_Trove\" title=\"Artifact Trove\">Artifact Trove</a> as a source.  Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: <a href=\"/Artifacts\" title=\"Artifacts\">Artifacts</a> are now liked by the <a href=\"/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">Dwarf</a> and <a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a>, disliked by all other NPCs.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artifacts\" title=\"Artifacts\">Artifacts</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Artifacts\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Amphibian_Fossil\" title=\"Amphibian Fossil\">Amphibian Fossil</a> • <a href=\"/Anchor\" title=\"Anchor\">Anchor</a> • <a href=\"/Ancient_Doll\" title=\"Ancient Doll\">Ancient Doll</a> • <a href=\"/Ancient_Drum\" title=\"Ancient Drum\">Ancient Drum</a> • <a class=\"mw-selfli