ol\">Prehistoric Tool</a> • <a href=\"/Prehistoric_Vertebra\" title=\"Prehistoric Vertebra\">Prehistoric Vertebra</a> • <a href=\"/Rare_Disc\" title=\"Rare Disc\">Rare Disc</a> • <a href=\"/Rusty_Cog\" title=\"Rusty Cog\">Rusty Cog</a> • <a href=\"/Rusty_Spoon\" title=\"Rusty Spoon\">Rusty Spoon</a> • <a href=\"/Rusty_Spur\" title=\"Rusty Spur\">Rusty Spur</a> • <a href=\"/Skeletal_Hand\" title=\"Skeletal Hand\">Skeletal Hand</a> • <a href=\"/Skeletal_Tail\" title=\"Skeletal Tail\">Skeletal Tail</a> • <a href=\"/Strange_Doll_(green)\" title=\"Strange Doll (green)\">Strange Doll (green)</a> • <a href=\"/Strange_Doll_(yellow)\" title=\"Strange Doll (yellow)\">Strange Doll (yellow)</a> • <a href=\"/Trilobite\" title=\"Trilobite\">Trilobite</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413230308\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.129 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.152 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2197/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 17652/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4022/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4647/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 561 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   61.282      1 -total\n 55.54%   34.036      1 Template:Infobox_artifact\n 27.47%   16.831     11 Template:Name\n 21.72%   13.310      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 21.24%   13.017      1 Template:Description\n  8.35%    5.118      3 Template:History\n  6.92%    4.243      1 Template:NavboxArtifacts\n  5.47%    3.352      3 Template:Version\n  3.33%    2.043      1 Template:Mainonly\n  2.97%    1.818      1 Template:Price\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1938-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413230307 and revision id 191958\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox artifact\n|image       = Ancient Seed.png\n|as          = <ul><li>[[Cindersap Forest]] (0.7%)</li><li>[[The Mountain]] (0.7%)</li></ul>\n|os          = {{Name|Fishing Treasure Chest|0.7-0.8%}}{{Name|Artifact Trove|3.7%}}{{Name|Deconstructor}}\n|md          = {{Name|Bug|0.5%}}{{Name|Cave Fly|0.5%}}{{Name|Grub|0.5%}}{{Name|Mutant Fly|0.5%}}{{Name|Mutant Grub|0.5%}}\n|dr          = <ul><li>{{Name|Ancient Seeds|1}}</li><li>&nbsp;[[File:AncientSeedsRecipe.png|24px]] Ancient Seeds Recipe</li></ul>\n|sellprice   = 5\n}}\n:''This article is about the artifact. For the fruit seed, see [[Ancient Seeds]].''\nThe '''Ancient Seed''' is an [[Artifacts|Artifact]] that can be found by digging up an [[Artifact Spot]] in [[Cindersap Forest]] or [[The Mountain]] (including the [[Quarry]]), or obtained inside [[Artifact Trove]]s, or [[Fishing#Treasure Chests|Fishing Treasure Chests]] after reaching [[Fishing#Fishing Skill|Fishing level 2]]. It can be dropped from [[Bug]]s, [[Grub]]s, [[Cave Fly|Cave Flies]], [[Mutant Fly|Mutant Flies]], and [[Mutant Grub]]s (0.5% chance). It can also be found by cutting foliage on [[Skull Cavern#Prehistoric Floors|Prehistoric Floors]], in [[The Mines]] when they are in a \"Dangerous\" state, or in the [[Volcano Dungeon]]<ref name=\"cosmeticplant_performtoolaction\"/>. Placing a packet of {{Name|Ancient Seeds|class=inline}} in a [[Deconstructor]] yields an Ancient Seed.\n\nThis artifact can be [[Crafting|crafted]] into viable [[Ancient Seeds|seeds]] that can be planted to grow [[Ancient Fruit]] during [[Spring]], [[Summer]] and [[Fall]], or during any season in the [[Greenhouse]] or the [[Ginger Island]] farm.\n\n==Donation==\nThe only productive use of the first Ancient Seed artifact found is to donate it to the [[Museum]]. The item contributes to the total count of Museum donations. [[Gunther]] will reward the player with one pack of plantable Ancient Seeds and the recipe to craft any further Ancient Seed artifacts into more seeds.\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Dwarf,Penny\n|dislike=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nAncient Seed is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Recipes==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Ingredients\n!Recipe From\n|-\n|[[File:Ancient Seeds.png]]\n|[[Ancient Seeds]]\n|Could these still grow?\n|{{Name|Ancient Seed|1}}\n|Donating [[Ancient Seed]] to the [[Museum]]\n|}\n\n==Tailoring==\nAncient Seed is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[File:Shirt237.png|24px]] [[Tailoring|Brown Suit]].\n\n==Quests==\nAncient Seed is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==References==\n<references>\n    <ref name=\"cosmeticplant_performtoolaction\">See <samp>StardewValley.TerrainFeatures.CosmeticPlant::performtoolaction</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.4|Updated sprite, added [[Artifact Trove]] as a source.  Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}\n{{History|1.5|[[Artifacts]] are now liked by the [[Dwarf]] and [[Penny]], disliked by all other NPCs.}}\n\n{{NavboxArtifacts}}\n\n[[de:Historisches Saatgut]]\n[[es:Semilla milenaria]]\n[[fr:Graine ancienne]]\n[[it:Seme antico]]\n[[ja:古代のタネ (発掘品)]]\n[[ko:고대 씨앗 (유물)]]\n[[hu:Ősi mag]]\n[[pt:Semente antiga]]\n[[ru:Древнее семя]]\n[[tr:Eski Tohum]]\n[[zh:古代种子]]"
    }
